{"tid":2253877,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"女學生被指藏士巴拿脫罪但堵路罪成 辯方曾質疑飛虎插贓嫁禍 官：警誠實可靠但細節有錯","createTime":"2020-10-22T12:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-23T17:39:38.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b8b8376b662b8d0866e51a1af8b1bfc4ce8fb960","tid":2253877,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:45:31.000Z","msg":"去年 11 月 13 日網民發起「大三罷」，兩輛輕型貨車被指當日在中大附近的沙田科學園路橫泊，堵塞交通。女學生及男售貨員被控在公眾地方造成阻礙，女學生另被指管有一支士巴拿，遭控以管有適合作非法用途工具意圖作非法用途罪，案件今（22 日）在沙田裁判法院裁決。飛虎隊警員曾供稱，女學生下車時孭着斜孭袋，內藏士巴拿；辯方則播放影片證明她無孭袋，質疑警插贓嫁禍。裁判官李志豪指，警員誠實可靠，但證供細節上「顯然有錯誤」，遂裁定該控罪不成立，但在公眾地方造成阻礙罪則罪成，押後判刑；男售貨員亦獲裁定罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/court/%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%97%8F%E5%A3%AB%E5%B7%B4%E6%8B%BF%E8%84%AB%E7%BD%AA%E4%BD%86%E5%A0%B5%E8%B7%AF%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E8%BE%AF%E6%96%B9%E6%9B%BE%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91%E9%A3%9B%E8%99%8E%E6%8F%92%E8%B4%93%E5%AB%81%E7%A6%8D-%E5%AE%98-%E8%AD%A6%E8%AA%A0%E5%AF%A6%E5%8F%AF%E9%9D%A0%E4%BD%86%E7%B4%B0%E7%AF%80%E6%9C%89%E9%8C%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E6%258B%25BF%25E8%2584%25AB%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E4%25BD%2586%25E5%25A0%25B5%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%25A3%259B%25E8%2599%258E%25E6%258F%2592%25E8%25B4%2593%25E5%25AB%2581%25E7%25A6%258D-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%258F%25AF%25E9%259D%25A0%25E4%25BD%2586%25E7%25B4%25B0%25E7%25AF%2580%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%258C%25AF%2F&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPd%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=28848c3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%2597%258F%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E6%258B%25BF%25